channel.title: Is it possible to make a webclient with this?

item.title: Is it possible to make a webclient with this?
item.dc:creator: @Gypsy Gypsy
item.description:
@Gypsy wrote:

You cannot have a webclient without a functioning client. I recommend downloading a new client that has a working client.java for you to edit and compile.

EDIT: You are making this webclient for a server you don’t own? Do they know this? If not you are going to need to get the full client with the cache files/java files.
